<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 15:26:07 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>我的猫梅布尔</title><link>https://some.pics/69f223084d2ae</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我的猫梅布尔！&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="My cat Mabel! " height="4032" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/chilli/69f223084d2ae.jpg" width="3024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://chilli.some.pics"&gt;@chilli&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 15:26:07 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>明亮午后</title><link>https://some.pics/69f21906e3178</link><description>&lt;p&gt;明亮的午后。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A bright pink bush in front of an East Modernist building. " height="3965" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/69f21906e3178.jpg" width="2233"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 14:43:22 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>黄昏海滩远眺</title><link>https://some.pics/69f206cde720f</link><description>&lt;p&gt;傍晚时分，在巴尔海滩眺望大海。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A night time photo, the moon up above in the sky, reflecting in the sea below and illuminating the sky below. A curved lookout point with metal railings is in the bottom of the photo with the horizon off in the distance." height="4012" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/tristy/69f206cde720f.jpg" width="3004"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://tristy.some.pics"&gt;@tristy&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 13:25:36 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>牙齿</title><link>https://some.pics/69f1fa197be01</link><description>&lt;p&gt;对不起，我无法处理这个请求。请提供完整的英文内容以便翻译。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt='A bag of hedgehog food featuring a hedgehog image with big front teeth, highlighting "wholesome nutrition" and benefits like vitamin E, high digestibility, and high protein.' height="6048" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/itsbrian/69f1fa197be01.jpg" width="8064"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://itsbrian.some.pics"&gt;@itsbrian&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 12:31:32 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>幻想生物般的栗树新叶</title><link>https://some.pics/69f1f7fa390f2</link><description>&lt;p&gt;它看起来几乎像一个奇幻生物，坐在柱子上伸出长长的手臂和手指，也许是想抓住什么、飞走，或者发起攻击……但这不过是栗树正在舒展它的叶子（而我的幻想又在作祟了）。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="As mentioned in the description: a b&amp;amp;w picture of a chestnut tree unfurling its leaves. " height="2865" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/69f1f7fa390f2.jpg" width="2517"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 12:22:20 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>